Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:02.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,劉備駕崩後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蜀國的諸葛孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為報先帝 起兵北伐
