Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:25.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兵法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:27.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey Ha！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明激起了KABE的鬥爭心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,此舉最終…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,令KABE覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:35.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我回來了 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在這裡說唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後也會一直說唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這才是我的真心誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全新classic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:47.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是KABE太人回歸舞台的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:52.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,同時也是KABE中了孔明計謀的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:55.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,輸家這樣說可能有些厚顏無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:01:00.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請隨我們一同 用音樂實現天下太平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很欣賞你 我願意加入你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要獻上對方想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:07.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪怕是敵人 也會主動找上來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這正是孫子的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:10.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兵法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:11.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歷經波折 得到新伙伴的月見英子
