Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:41.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都是明日的超級明星 今晚一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放下不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,自從KABE加入後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,客人明顯更有激情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:03:00.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的 KABE語言的感染力是毋庸置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,客人上傳的照片也遠超以前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:07.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這下10萬讚企劃應該就有戲唱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:07.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,演唱會的品質跟計劃能否成功無關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:15.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後需要更加縝密的戰略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（天下太平之計 vol.1）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:23.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來將舉辦第一屆「10萬讚企劃對策會議」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這人總是穿成那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 請翻開手上資料的第4頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏季的大型音樂節SUMMER SONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:40.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,參加前提是通過10萬讚企劃 詳細訊息在這一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:43.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須用候選者本人的SNS帳號發布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是多條投稿的累計數量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而是單一投稿要達到10萬讚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:52.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,投稿內容可由候選者自行決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,距離截止日還剩20天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,目前已有多位歌手報名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其中率先博得10萬讚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（100,000讚獲得！！確定出場）\N其中率先博得10萬讚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（100,000讚獲得！！確定出場）\N將獲得SUMMER SONIA的出場權
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:02.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（100,000讚獲得！！確定出場）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順便說一下 目前的有力候選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這三組
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,憑藉融合電子舞曲和JPOP風格的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,博得人氣的二人組
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,ICE BORN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正統搖滾樂團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Salesio帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後是深受年輕人喜愛的女子樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:18.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,ICE BORN都拿到6萬讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,第二名Salesio帝國都有4萬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,徹底落後了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須趕緊發點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在還不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天時 地利 人和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:39.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,行事之時 必須判斷好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且 ICE BORN不會再漲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:47.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我分析了近兩週的讚數推移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果顯示 這5天幾乎是水平推移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也就是說 宣傳已經飽和了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,過早投稿適得其反了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,同理 第二名Salesio帝國也到頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,似乎除了核心粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其他人轉發的數量太少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而真正需要提防的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,目前位於第三名的AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,AZALEA？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:19.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,主唱久遠七海擁有極佳的唱功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過可怕的不是唱功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在她們背後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:27.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有大型事務所KEY TIME支撐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:28.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KEY TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,據說為了捧紅旗下藝人 甚至會鋌而走險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是那家KEY TIME嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有個熟人在他們那 也被單方面解約了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好傳聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:43.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而能用於宣傳的資金和人才 是我們的幾百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果不想辦法對付她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就無法通往SUMMER SONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就更該儘早行動了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你究竟準備什麼時候行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:56.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超過她們 以最快速度博得10萬讚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,投稿的日子就在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,投稿的日子就在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,截止日的三天前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,三天前？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們將這一天設為X日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這未免太趕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有 你到底想怎樣博得10萬讚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-就是啊 -失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,計策當然有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 在談計謀前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:21.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:25.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請你先跟赤兔馬功夫來個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,赤兔馬是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說唱對決時不就在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 那個解說的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他跟你約戰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要在X日前來一場說唱對決大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為其他事分心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是無法發揮出最佳表演狀態的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以你現在的狀態 可以前往更高的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:57.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（「10萬讚企劃」成功之路）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（「10萬讚企劃」成功之路）\N而這個計謀的關鍵就在於
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:05.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,決勝的歌曲就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:10.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（六本木烏龍麵店（暫定））
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（反反覆覆的Every day）\N（六本木烏龍麵店（暫定））
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（反反覆覆的Every day）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼時候寫了這首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（連哭泣都忘了）\N什麼時候寫了這首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（連哭泣都忘了）\N可現在只有試聽音源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可現在只有試聽音源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,距離截止日還有兩週多點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能在期限內完成足以博得10萬讚的歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,厲害的編曲家和錄音棚都到位了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:35.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能道破本質 刺激觀眾心靈的KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再加上能撼動靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:40.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打動聽眾心靈的英子的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,博得10萬讚比翻扇子還簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:45.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,此計名為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:50.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（天下太平之計 vol.1）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天下太平之計 vol.1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我定會讓英子的歌聲響徹天下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拯救迷茫蒼生的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:04.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蒼生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蒼生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不掃清心中的霧霾沒辦法戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 去練練感染力以備決戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 我去完善下這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他們真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:24.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們也需要進化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吉他就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聲音也就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,身體也就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:44.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這還是我第一次把歌曲錄成音源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我無法陪你去錄音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過我可以送你這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼 可以打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行 請在你感到不安時再打開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一定能幫上你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上面有編號 請按照順序使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:10.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一定要按照編號順序打開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要感到不安再打開啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,1 應買兩個極大特惠Q彈布丁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,2 道路使用許可申請書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,3 澀谷SKY SQUARE展望台門票？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好 看不懂是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之…先買布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我答應赤兔馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要炒麵麵包和可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,昨天不是也請過你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,佐藤 你也配頂嘴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少廢話 趕緊去買
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們願意跟你這種凡人當朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還不好好感謝我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,趕緊去買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最近回歸的 是叫KABE吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那傢伙真就只有技術行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:16.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽完一點共鳴都沒有 驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即興說唱的連勝只是運氣好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,陰沉的凡人逞起威風來太難堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:27.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,燕雀安知鴻鵠之志哉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想必小鳥無法理解翱翔天際的鳳凰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼事呢 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是赤壁開戰前 跟吳舌戰時說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都獲得鋼鐵心臟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,何為真正的強大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那自然是…臂力之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:04.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,靠臂力真能拯救人民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:09.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,徒有其表的強大可不是真正的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 有警察
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也太難堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是來錄音的月見英子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是月見英子 藝名EIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是Steave Kido
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（栗屋的美味 超好吃 筍乾）\N世界最強的帥筍乾DJ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要筍乾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在錄音棚吃筍乾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是超爽的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好像在哪裡見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Steave Kido？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:39.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個在洛杉磯和伊維薩島演出過的日本DJ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:43.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個在三年前的SUMMER SONIA上 向觀眾砸了一堆蛋糕的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是本尊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,叫我Kid吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都是這樣叫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Kid先生是那位Kid先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪個Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有很多Kid的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比如怪盜Kid 比如格鬥家Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比如醫療kit？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 要吐槽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後 你的經紀人孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這人真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是在哪裡找來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪個…就是在附近找的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他該不會是真正的孔明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我沒見過本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Kid先生跟孔明聊過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我跟他賭了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要能寫出我接受的歌就免費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:33.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是寫不出來 孔明就當我的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可沒聽他說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明為什麼要答應這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順便問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正常委託你需要多少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,突然委託我 而且是專門服務你兩週
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,需要1000萬左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:49.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,1000…這哪付得起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我就是沒幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你今天可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拜託了 我沒多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以現在開始錄音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:03.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我沒那心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,極大特惠Q彈布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兩個可以都給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以 請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,筍乾布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:27.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在錄音棚吃筍乾布丁爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:29.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這吃東西的品味…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就開始幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,得對得起你的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幫上忙了 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你寫的歌我聽過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要來賭一把嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱你喜歡的瑪麗亞·迪賽兒的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,試著打動我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是我有幹勁了 就做價值超過布丁的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞·迪賽兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我崇拜的歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:04.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,給了我契機 讓我想當歌手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我願意唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:07.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請讓我唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歌曲就選…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,《I'm still alive today》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在要是逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想參加SUMMER SONIA就是痴人說夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:26.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事的 這首歌我都唱過幾百遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:27.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,非常有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是自學的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:43.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞·迪賽兒的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,儘管唱的是日常的點滴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,卻透著一股宗教韻味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有向神祈禱的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有節奏藍調和靈魂樂風格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:58.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最近還有融合了電子舞曲和浩室的曲風
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她總是在不斷摸索表現方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:02.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論是以前的歌還是現在的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽你唱過我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那你是有幹勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你缺乏自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,派對咖孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:23.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不陪英子去沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我將妙計交給英子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是趙雲去保護劉備時 你交給他的錦囊妙計吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:34.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但這不是兒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣真能贏過AZALEA這個對手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:43.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原石要經過打磨才能變成玉石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:48.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這場試煉 英子必定也能攻克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:52.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對此堅信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你缺乏自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在你的歌聲中 聽不出你是怎樣一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在你找到自我前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你用不著來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我必須在兩週內完成這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你得抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我逃避不再
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新生代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:17.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,敗者沒有人權
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:23.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣是沒辦法戰勝赤兔馬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,赤兔馬比那時更強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要戰勝他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就需要更有衝擊力的歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:45.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,徒有其表的強大可不是真正的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,簡直莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,氣死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,氣死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,至於說成那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也知道自己還遠遠不到家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是 我必須完成這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:04.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣才能找到自我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明給我的計謀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路使用申請書 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是要我在街頭演出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,演出的人還真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說我還從沒在街頭演出過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好位置都被占了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在哪演好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Everything seemed to be alright）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:58.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Cause you gave me whispers of love all night）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:58.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Uh-）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:18:59.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Uh-）\N唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Uh-）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:00.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Uh-）\N但不是刻意想唱好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But I'm alone tonight）\N但不是刻意想唱好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But I'm alone tonight）\N能強烈感受到想唱歌的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能強烈感受到想唱歌的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:05.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（And I don't know how to stop heaving sighs）\N能強烈感受到想唱歌的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（And I don't know how to stop heaving sighs）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（And I don't know how to stop heaving sighs）\N抱歉 可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:10.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你有道路使用許可書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行 得申請到許可才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:20.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-你叫什麼 有證明身份的證件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-怎麼辦\N-你叫什麼 有證明身份的證件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:22.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-你叫什麼 有證明身份的證件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想…有駕照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,許可書拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:38.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,算了 有許可就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可別唱太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 辛苦警官了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 給你添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很想多聽聽你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了 急死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼是你急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你也是來街頭演出的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過是第一次來 有點怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才的警官在看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還在懷疑我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說 你會彈吉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就一起演出吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:20.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱什麼歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才那首《I'm still alive today》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好啊 來唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不了 我想聽你唱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:30.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Everything seemed to be alright）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:56.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Cause you gave me whispers of love all night）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Uh-）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:02.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But I'm alone tonight）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:07.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（And I don't know how to stop heaving sighs）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:07.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（And I don't know how to stop heaving sighs）\N你這段時間一直在占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你這段時間一直在占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I just wanna get you out of my mind）\N結果不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:11.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I just wanna get you out of my mind）\N不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I just wanna get you out of my mind）\N這一卦是吉是凶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（You don't know how much I love you）\N這一卦是吉是凶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（You don't know how much I love you）\N現在還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But you don't wanna be with me any more）\N現在還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:16.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But you don't wanna be with me any more）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But you don't wanna be with me any more）\N只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（But you don't wanna be with me any more）\N命運難免坎坷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I'm still alive today）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:25.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（You are so far away）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:31.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Even though you have broken my heart baby）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:34.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I'm still alive today）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（And miss you all day）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I just thought I could not live without you）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（I just thought I could not live without you）\N好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:41.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要繼續一起演出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:45.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好主意 演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想聽聽你唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:49.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是月見英子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,叫我英子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼…你就叫我七海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請多指教 七海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:02.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好敵手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:07.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竟然算出了「斷琴之交」的卦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（天下太平之計 vol.1）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:15.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:17.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來段心情上好↑↑的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:21.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,針丟地上 音樂響起 派對之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來 大家一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:27.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hip-Pop People
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:31.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,撥打那奇蹟Number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yo！在這時代分享的MUSIC
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:40.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想將其找出 轉動地球儀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:44.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生活動盪不穩 所以要重視平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:47.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生活並非全是好事 所以「還能拼！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,踢開糟糕的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:50.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,按下重啟的按鈕！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,DJ 音樂響起來！！此刻TRIP
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:56.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟隨前沿的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:23:01.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用心感受 搖擺起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:05.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來段心情上好↑↑的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:11.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乘著浪 全力跳躍 舞蹈之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:15.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來 大家一起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:16.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hip-Pop People
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:22.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直至天亮 奇蹟Number
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:29.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:36.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah